      <item>
        <title>Delete tag after Successful action</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[agiletortoise]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>There’s not a similar convenience feature to remove tags, but it can be done with a quick script at the end of your action, try this in a script step at the end of the action, editing the “TAG-NAME” placeholder:</p>
<pre><code class="lang-javascript">draft.removeTag("TAG-NAME");
draft.update();
</code></pre>
          <p><a href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/t/delete-tag-after-successful-action/7908/2">Read full topic</a></p>
        ]]></description>
